    My name is Jason Duraj. I am the owner and founder of FloridasBestRealtor.Net. I am a local real estate developer, seasoned real estate agent, and mortgage broker. I have worked very hard over the last 19 years in the Real Estate business to build an outstanding relationship with my colleagues, clients and top professionals in the industry. We are a LOCAL full-service real estate brokerage office. We will guide you and advise you in every step of home buying or selling process. We will carefully negotiate every deal on your behalf to get you the best possible result and greatest savings in your wallet.
